    <h1>Why Open Source?</h1>
      <p>RedHat believes in making technology more accessible for all people. By using an open source model, we share our software models publicly for all to access. This contributes to a more collaborative ecosystem in the tech space. Additionally, we stay at the forefront of innovation by incorporating diverse perspectives and ideas from the community.</p>      
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="story">
    <h2>Customer Priority</h2>
        <p>At RedHat, our customers are at the heart of everything we do. We prioritize their needs and feedback, ensuring that our open-source solutions are not only innovative but also practical and user-friendly. With an open source model, our work is easily accessible to our customers, allowing for authentic feedback throughout the design process.</p>      
  </section>

